title: The Keys to Elfin Enchantment: Mastery of the Faerie Light Through the Portals of Manifestation
description: THE KEYS TO ELFIN ENCHANTMENT by The Silver Elves is a book of enchantment, for enchanters, revealing the Keys to Enchantment, the true and greatest magic of the elfin folk. It is filled with the philosophy of the elves and how they encounter and subtly transform the world wielding and fulfilling its dreams and desires while guiding it toward a better and more elfin future. Do you seek to charm the world and obtain all that you desire in the deepest recesses of your heart and soul? The Silver Elves reveal the ancient pathway toward success and fulfillment through enchantment.
author: The Silver Elves
